# vscode-extension/.env
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VSCE credentials for publish.sh — DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE
#
# How to get a VSCE_PAT:
#   1. Sign in to https://dev.azure.com  (use the Microsoft account linked to
#      the VS Code Marketplace publisher "CurtisFranks")
#   2. User Settings → Personal Access Tokens → New Token
#   3. Organization: All accessible organizations
#   4. Scopes: Marketplace → Manage   (custom, not Full Access)
#   5. Copy the token — it is shown only once.
#
# Paste it below and save. Never push this file.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VSCE_PAT=paste-your-azure-devops-pat-here
